imdb.plot outline: It travels in every episode in search of the small towns of Catalonia. It is inspired by the Danish program Comedy on the Edge. The main goal of the foraster is to find in two days the best people to be able to create a 45-minute monologue that will present in a fun way the habitants of the village. This way, the protagonists of the program are simply the habitants. The program tries to claim the particularity and the familiar essence of those small villages.
imdb.title: El foraster
plot: It travels in every episode in search of the small towns of Catalonia. It is inspired by the Danish program Comedy on the Edge. The main goal of the foraster is to find in two days the best people to be able to create a 45-minute monologue that will present in a fun way the habitants of the village. This way, the protagonists of the program are simply the habitants. The program tries to claim the particularity and the familiar essence of those small villages.
